@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

title TunSociety - Platform Use Case Diagram

actor Guest
actor Member

rectangle "TunSociety Platform" {
  usecase "Browse guest pages" as UC_Browse
  usecase "Register" as UC_Register
  usecase "Log in" as UC_Login

  usecase "View feed" as UC_Feed
  usecase "Create post" as UC_CreatePost
  usecase "Update own post" as UC_UpdatePost
  usecase "Delete own post" as UC_DeletePost
  usecase "Comment on post" as UC_Comment
  usecase "React to post" as UC_React

  usecase "Manage profile" as UC_Profile
  usecase "Update display name" as UC_UpdateDisplayName

  usecase "Search workspace" as UC_Search
  usecase "View search results" as UC_SearchResults
  usecase "Open member profile" as UC_OpenMemberProfile

  usecase "Send friend request" as UC_SendRequest
  usecase "Respond to friend request" as UC_RespondRequest

  usecase "View notifications" as UC_Notifications
  usecase "Mark notifications read" as UC_ReadNotifications

  usecase "View messenger" as UC_Messenger
  usecase "Send direct message" as UC_SendDM

  usecase "Evaluate submitted text" as UC_Evaluate
}

Guest --> UC_Browse
Guest --> UC_Register
Guest --> UC_Login

Member --> UC_Feed
Member --> UC_CreatePost
Member --> UC_UpdatePost
Member --> UC_DeletePost
Member --> UC_Comment
Member --> UC_React
Member --> UC_Profile
Member --> UC_UpdateDisplayName
Member --> UC_Search
Member --> UC_SearchResults
Member --> UC_OpenMemberProfile
Member --> UC_SendRequest
Member --> UC_RespondRequest
Member --> UC_Notifications
Member --> UC_ReadNotifications
Member --> UC_Messenger
Member --> UC_SendDM

UC_Search .> UC_SearchResults : <<include>>
UC_SearchResults .> UC_OpenMemberProfile : <<extend>>

UC_Register .> UC_Evaluate : <<include>>
UC_CreatePost .> UC_Evaluate : <<include>>
UC_UpdatePost .> UC_Evaluate : <<include>>
UC_Comment .> UC_Evaluate : <<include>>
UC_UpdateDisplayName .> UC_Evaluate : <<include>>
UC_SendRequest .> UC_Evaluate : <<include>>
UC_SendDM .> UC_Evaluate : <<include>>

note bottom
Current search categories are users, posts, and events placeholder.
Jobs, groups, products, and similar filters can be added later
without changing the overall search interaction pattern.
end note
@enduml
